#[ignore = "open question: [MS-OI29500] §2.1.275 (ISO 29500-1 §17.9.1, §17.18.10) — Word will not load a negative abstractNumId; validate() reports ok=true. REAL GAP: stemma parses ST_DecimalNumber as signed and does not range-check abstractNumId. Pending confirmation against real Word."]
